---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact — System Report" description="Get in touch with the System Report editorial team — story tips, corrections, advertising inquiries, and general questions.">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-6">
      Contact
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-gray dark:prose-invert max-w-none prose-headings:font-serif prose-a:text-blue-600 dark:prose-a:text-blue-400">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        We read every message. The fastest way to reach the System Report editorial team is by email.
      </p>

      <div class="not-prose my-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">Email</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <a href="mailto:contact@systemreport.net" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-medium">contact@systemreport.net</a>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            We aim to respond within two business days.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-2">Mailing Address</h2>
          <address class="not-italic text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            System Report<br />
            Barbaros Mah. Begonya Sk.<br />
            Nidakule Ataşehir Batı No: 1/2<br />
            34758 Ataşehir, İstanbul<br />
            Türkiye
          </address>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>What to write about</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Story tips</strong> — Have something we should be covering? Send a brief summary and any relevant links. Confidentiality is respected on request.</li>
        <li><strong>Corrections</strong> — If you spot a factual error, point us to the article and the specific claim. We post corrections promptly and transparently.</li>
        <li><strong>Press &amp; product briefings</strong> — Embargoed announcements, product reviews, and pre-briefings are welcome. Please include the embargo time in the subject line.</li>
        <li><strong>Advertising</strong> — Sponsorship and partnership inquiries should include your company name, target audience, and proposed timing.</li>
        <li><strong>Permissions</strong> — Republication, syndication, and translation requests are reviewed case by case.</li>
        <li><strong>Privacy</strong> — Questions about how this site handles data are answered in our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What we don't do</h2>

      <p>
        System Report does not provide tech support for products we cover, individual investment or legal advice, or paid placement disguised as editorial. Pitches that ignore these boundaries are not answered.
      </p>

      <h2>Editorial independence</h2>

      <p>
        Our editorial decisions are made independently of advertisers, sponsors, and the companies we cover. If a piece is sponsored, that relationship is disclosed clearly in the article itself.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
